      *                  * Determinazione imponibile                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-fit-iva-ibl (1)   to   w-gen-ibl-rda          .
           multiply  rf-fit-pib-rda       by   w-gen-ibl-rda
                                        giving w-gen-ibl-abb          .
           divide    100                  into w-gen-ibl-abb
                                               rounded                .
           subtract  w-gen-ibl-abb        from w-gen-ibl-rda          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione ritenuta                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-fit-per-rda       to   w-gen-ali-rda          .
           move      zero                 to   w-gen-imp-rda          .
           multiply  w-gen-ali-rda        by   w-gen-ibl-rda
                                        giving w-gen-imp-rda          .
           divide    100                  into w-gen-imp-rda
                                               rounded                .
